---
/** Section 00 — the thesis. The category claim, stated once, in huge type.
 *  Everything after it is evidence. */
---

<section class="thesis wrap" id="thesis" data-scene>
  <div class="thesis-lines">
    <p class="thesis-line">Every computer is about to run AI agents.</p>
    <p class="thesis-line">None of them have an operating system.</p>
    <p class="thesis-line thesis-punch">Unicity AOS is that <span class="gradient-text">operating system</span>.</p>
  </div>
  <p class="thesis-note prose dim">
    When software multiplied, the operating system won the era, because
    applications needed one safe place to share the machine. Agents are the
    new applications. They need one safe place to share tools, memory, and
    trust. The capsule registry is the planned app store for that layer:
    open, signed, and owned by no model vendor.
  </p>
</section>

